clishell.plugins

Class TeeWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.Writer
      • clishell.plugins.TeeWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.io.Flushable, java.lang.Appendable, java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public class TeeWriter
extends java.io.Writer
    Inspired by the Unix "tee" command, this Writer will send everything written to it to any number of other writers that are registered with it.
    Author:
    mross
